{
  "stem": "23131.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That they were saying, what will we do with food?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How will we feed them?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That time, it wasn't organized.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When they chose my husband as a commander, it was already the seven people that I mentioned.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then they went into a meeting and they chose him as a commander because he had military knowledge, he served in the Polish Army, he was good in languages, he was good in speech, and he was good in organizing.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was the oldest.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they-- they choosed him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But-- so each one that came from the ghetto, they were afraid.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Maybe he will take away a piece from me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Maybe he will take away a piece from me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was-- they didn't click together.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't say they didn't trust.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were afraid that-- that they'll take away from him something.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe it will be my-- maybe we'll get less soup by-- by some other people coming than-- than he used to, you know?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a-- it was a kitchen for everybody.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a kitchen for the-- for the special milk for the children, more.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But for the elderly, he tried to pay more attention, you know, like, to give them a bigger supply.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they were afraid that each one-- that they'll take away from me something.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe it won't be enough for me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And people are funny.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They're-- if you want to live, why shouldn't I now want to live?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So how did Tuvia cope with that?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very, very hard.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "With other Jewish people, it's not easy to go because we have our ideas.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We have our mindset.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And very-- it's very hard sometimes to-- to cope with them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not-- very-- they gave him a lot of trouble.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
